OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWet and windy weather will move
OL,6,Fsoutheast across Scotland and Northern
OL,7,FIreland this morning into the north
OL,8,Fand west of England and Wales this
OL,9,Fafternoon. Southeast England remaining
OL,10,Fdry and bright. Turning brighter with
OL,11,Fblustery showers in the northwest
OL,12,Flater.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCentral and southern England
OL,15,Fand Wales will have rain overnight.
OL,16,FElsewhere there will be clear spells,
OL,17,Fbut with blustery showers in the far
OL,18,Fnorth and northwest. Mild and frost-
OL,19,Ffree.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
