OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCentral and southern England
OL,6,Fand Wales will hold onto outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain on Friday, heaviest in the west
OL,8,Flater. Brighter elsewhere with a few
OL,9,Fshowers. Mild, with mostly gentle
OL,10,Fwinds.
